d=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Bl6jJcwCccQQ7kNvgExhh8A&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB8U-0B-u7ZG37_AexI_uULeIv-D93YrZD-6PxCxGpb7Q&oe=66D30BF7"}, "display_name": "T-ON FITNESS", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# For a more realistic and immersive experience in VR!\n# Now, anytime and anywhere\n# Active Life is T-ON\n\n\u3164\n\n# Website : https://vr.tioncare.com/\n\n\n# Discord : https://discord.gg/m4MmxKqh\n\n\n\u3164\n# Episode 2 Japan Release \ud83c\udf89\n- Adventure: New scenario added\n- Fitness: New workout moves and map added\n- Meditation: New meditation and yoga moves added\n{1208344610482069}\n{890797932886928}\n{473226985446786}\n{523504060129865}\nYou can check the purchase screen after selecting Adventure Island in T-ON Fitness!\n{3877865252539751}\n\n\u3164\n# Customized workout programs you can only experience at T-ON!\n- Choose from a variety of content in three concepts, Adventure, Fitness, and Meditation to enhance your workout enjoyment with the content that suits you best!\n{471515915482331}\n\n# Adventure with T-ON Friends!\n- Adventure mode where you enjoy clearing scenarios and missions with T-ON Friends!\n\n\n- Comprising a running-focused Activity mode and a turn-based Stage mode, enjoy without boredom and boost your workout effectiveness!\n{1009916523615167}\n\n# High-intensity fitness with your personal trainer, KIKI!\n- Fitness mode enjoyed with coaching from your personal trainer, KIKI!\n- Based on the user's fitness assessment results, the six customized exercise programs for different physical factors reduce the risk of injury and make workouts more efficient!\n{1302146471170825}\n\n# Cool down meditation for the relaxation of body and mind!\n- Meditation mode combining cool-down stretches and mindfulness relaxation after workouts! \n- Embark on a journey to find peace of mind, experiencing the effects of step-by-step meditation against beautiful backdrops such as sunsets, the sea, and campfires\n{868676071769341}", "short_description": "Experience Unique Healthcare with T-ON Fitness!\nNow, enjoy T-ON Care's personalized exercise programs in VR"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "\uc5b4\ub4dc\ubca4\ucc98_\uc77c\ubcf82.png", "id": "1956183801523023", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003224_1956183804856356_4156409700116056171_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fC6m5TYtckoQ7kNvgG2OD12&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA1Q7YdMAz45wHhpElRDk2hFwKLIWpLuONYO5dhkdokQQ&oe=66D2FDAD"}, {"file_name": "\uc5b4\ub4dc\ubca4\ucc98_\uc77c\ubcf8.png", "id": "1616630038908222", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982676_1616630042241555_1234258292738228956_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vlJNozBF0ScQ7kNvgEdTuUZ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDIhXnU9ZzUQlMIRCB0vtZmkoMKZEEGT_1E78XyXaiUqg&oe=66D31589"}, {"file_name": "\ud53c\ud2b81.png", "id": "1611526779641449", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75287553_1611526782974782_6104676734363015199_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YHuQ5eAFUh4Q7kNvgF50MdJ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBNhvS-9xOlCKhpZaZLNsAyu_k3AbIqFL73fbJ-i5AjSA&oe=66D3196F"}, {"file_name": "\uba54\ub5141.png", "id": "1536340803954928", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262741_1536340807288261_741120748059442881_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Y-7zx8CSBx8Q7kNvgFmtbjB&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBvebE60674RDCadYpXpezvqyRwDPA1TxFKgAKSr59SYg&oe=66D2FD86"}, {"file_name": "\uc5d0\ud53c\uc18c\ub4dc-\uc120\ud0dd.png", "id": "1228511945000610", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974463_1228511948333943_3272947843242231154_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=p_AksKJgXHkQ7kNvgGOFwC4&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com